-- Verivox Website Will Offer Finance Products, Handelsblatt Says
-- B y   C o r n e l i u s   R a h n
-- 2012-09-05T06:59:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-05/verivox-website-will-offer-finance-products-handelsblatt-says.html
Verivox GmbH, a German price-
comparison website, has started to compare and broker financial
products, to offset dropping revenue from its electricity
business,  Handelsblatt  reported, citing Chief Executive Officer
Chris Oehlund.  The company is initially offering services for overnight
money,  time deposits  and car insurance and may add further
financial instruments, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Cornelius Rahn in Frankfurt at 
 crahn2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Kenneth Wong at 
 kwong11@bloomberg.net  